snippet.title: FRAMED Game - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY FRAMED NOW! https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/framed/id886565180?at=10lLxc

FRAMED is a multi-award winning noir puzzle game, where you re-arrange panels of a comic book to change the outcome of the story.
